sourcesContent:
import { Box, Grid, Stack, Typography } from '@mui/material';

function PersonalInformation() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#fff', padding: '10px' }}>
      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center' }}>
        <Typography
          variant="h5"
          gutterBottom
          sx={{
            fontFamily: 'SVN-Sofia-Medium',
            fontWeight: 500,
            fontSize: '20px',
            margin: 0,
          }}
        >
          Personal Information
        </Typography>
        <Typography
          variant="body2"
          gutterBottom
          sx={{
            fontFamily: 'SVN-Sofia-Medium',
            color: 'rgb(104, 112, 118)',
            display: 'flex',
            alignItems: 'center',
            margin: 0,
          }}
        >
          Required  (
          <Typography variant="body1" gutterBottom sx={{ fontSize: '16px', color: 'rgb(229, 72, 77)', margin: 0 }}>
            *
          </Typography>
          )
        </Typography>
      </Box>
      <hr
        style={{
          margin: '10px 0',
          borderWidth: '0px 0px thin',
          borderColor: 'rgba(193, 200, 205, 0.24)',
          borderStyle: 'solid',
        }}
      />
      <form>
        <Stack direction="column" spacing={2}>
          <Grid spacing={2}>
            <Grid xs={8}>
              <Typography
                variant="body2"
                gutterBottom
                sx={{
                  fontFamily: 'SVN-Sofia-Medium',
                  color: 'rgb(104, 112, 118)',
                  display: 'flex',
                  alignItems: 'center',
                  margin: 0,
                }}
              >
                Name
                <Typography
                  variant="body1"
                  gutterBottom
                  sx={{ fontSize: '16px', color: 'rgb(229, 72, 77)', margin: 0 }}
                >
                  *
                </Typography>
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid xs={4}></Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Stack>
        <Stack direction="row" spacing={2}>
          <Grid spacing={2}>
            <Grid xs={8}>
              <Typography
                variant="body2"
                gutterBottom
                sx={{
                  fontFamily: 'SVN-Sofia-Medium',
                  color: 'rgb(104, 112, 118)',
                  display: 'flex',
                  alignItems: 'center',
                  margin: 0,
                }}
              >
                Name
                <Typography
                  variant="body1"
                  gutterBottom
                  sx={{ fontSize: '16px', color: 'rgb(229, 72, 77)', margin: 0 }}
                >
                  *
                </Typography>
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid xs={4}></Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Stack>
      </form>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default PersonalInformation;
